@page "/"

<PageTitle>Issue Tester - Home</PageTitle>

<div class="max-w-3xl space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Issue Tester</h1>

    <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        This application is used to reproduce and test issues reported by users against
        BlazorBlueprint components. Each issue gets its own page under <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm">/issues/</code>.
    </p>

    <div class="rounded-lg border border-border p-6 space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">How to add a new issue reproduction</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
            <li>Create a new Razor page in <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm">Components/Pages/Issues/</code></li>
            <li>Use the route <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm">@@page "/issues/&lt;issue-number&gt;"</code></li>
            <li>Add the minimal code needed to reproduce the issue</li>
            <li>Add a link to the navigation in <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm">Components/Layout/MainLayout.razor</code> if desired</li>
            <li>Run the app with <code class="rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm">dotnet run</code></li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-lg border border-border p-6 space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Issue Pages</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-muted-foreground">
            <li><a href="/issues/131" class="text-primary underline hover:no-underline">#131</a> - Nested button group / dialog trigger styling bug</li>
            <li><a href="/issues/132" class="text-primary underline hover:no-underline">#132</a> - File input crashes on file select</li>
            <li><a href="/issues/example" class="text-primary underline hover:no-underline">Example Issue</a> - Template showing how to structure a reproduction</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
